Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I just, you know,
look at it for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an artist, Sid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're telling me
you're just gonna walk out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm never going
to see it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a good chance
of that, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Most guys, you know,
for the first one,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,they start
with something small.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mom," girlfriend's initials,
something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.92,0:00:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a full set of sleeves,
all in a couple of months.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Takes guys a few years
to get the ink you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have
a few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.64,0:01:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish to hell I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The vault. Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.91,0:02:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't. The branch
manager's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.20,0:02:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-Where is he?
-It's lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's at White Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,White Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fast food restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They serve
those little square burgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.05,0:02:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have a half
a million dollars cash in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think
it would be better...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.57,0:02:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are completely surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.91,0:02:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.66,0:02:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Put down your weapons now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarely in the case
of armed robbery
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,do we hear a plea
of no contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this,
Mr. Scofield?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:02:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Honor, we'd like
to recess if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My client's a bit confused
at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He is, Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you should heed
your representation's advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,take some additional time
to consider your response.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.35,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already done that,
Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.19,0:03:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll retire to my chambers
to determine sentencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Court's recessed until 1:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you
to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not gonna
take this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you blame him?
He's your nephew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's beginning
to get the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.18,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that anybody
he attaches himself to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is gonna
end up in prison...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's not the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,who's starting to feel
that way, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you give us a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:03:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You just put the book
in that woman's hand
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.45,0:04:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and she's gonna lob it
at you like a grenade.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice and punishment
are the same thing to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then will you please tell me
what's going through your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known you
my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have
a violent bone in your body,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and I know you didn't
need the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Veronica.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you
let me help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My whole life, you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've gotta let me
deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Given your lack
of prior criminal conduct,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am inclined
toward probation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the fact that
you discharged a deadly weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,during the commission
of the crime suggests malice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason,
I find it incumbent
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,that you see the inside
of a prison cell, Mr. Scofield.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here
that you've requested to be incarcerated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere near your home
here in Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to honor that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The closest
level one facility to--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Level one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's maximum security,
Your Honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would ask counsel to refrain
from interrupting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As I was saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the closest
level one facility
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,would be Fox River
State Penitentiary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the term
of your sentence,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm setting it
at five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be eligible for parole
in half that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sentence to be carried out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, step inside the door
and check yourself for bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,When you hear
the knock, step out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the line moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We ain't got all day
to get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.24,0:05:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's go. Move it.
- No more talking in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it. You got less
than five minutes to take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep the line moving.
Keep it moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Move it. Right now. Let's go. Move, move.
- Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Name and back number.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Scofield, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,94941.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you
a religious man, Scofield?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Never really
thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, 'cause
the Ten Commandments
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.80,0:05:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,don't mean
a box of piss in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We got two commandments
and two only.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The first commandment
is you got nothing coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the second commandment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:05:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See commandment number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You talking out the side
of your neck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, are you
being a smartass?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Just trying to fly low,
avoid the radar, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do my time... and get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't any flying
under my radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, can a brother
get some air conditioning up here, cuz?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hotter than
a crack ho's mouth, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with the AC, man.
Give me the crack ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.79,0:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You look kind of pretty
to be up in here, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.83,0:07:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I suggest you
take a seat, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.50,0:07:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't nothing to do up in here
but serve time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't nobody
gonna serve it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to
Prisneyland, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...is now
on mandatory lockdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna talk
about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's not
worth talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's keeping you up,
it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.77,0:08:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.94,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You did the best you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He just sort of rolled over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't put up a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I shouldn't
be talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, if it's on your mind,
it's on your mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,All wings, guard coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All wings,
guard coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Trey Street Deuces
got the hoops.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nortenos got the bleachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.31,0:08:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Woods got the weight pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The C.O.s got the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, the guards
are the dirtiest gang in this whole place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The only difference
between us and them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:08:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,is the badge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's the pet lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll deny it,
but he's D.B. Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Parachuted out of a plane
30 years ago with a million and a half in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't look
like the type.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Who does?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What up, Wholesale?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-You okay?
-Gonna be greater later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What you doing
with this fish, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-He's my new cellie.
-Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wholesale's got it wired up
at the commissary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.01,0:09:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you want,
he can get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep
handing out my jacket,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'm gonna
bust your grape.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.81,0:09:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you couldn't bust a grape in Napa
with a set of cleats on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,-What are you talking about?
-Man, you want to bump your gums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.77,0:09:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no. Now you're
talking, talking, talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Guy named Lincoln Burrows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Linc the Sink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That what
they're calling him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.35,0:10:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,As in, he'll come at you
with everything but the kitchen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Snowflake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Where can I find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Man killed
the Vice President's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,In a month,
he's getting the chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,which means no one up this river
is more dangerous than him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause he's got
nothing to lose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they gonna do?
Kill him twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There a way
I can get to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. The only time
those boys get out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.41,0:10:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is for chapel and P.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,P.I.? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Prison Industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys that get along
get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, painting, scrapping,
making mattresses, you name it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't get excited, though,
if I were you, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You ain't sniffin'
none of P.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.55,0:10:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.76,0:10:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause John Abruzzi runs it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,"John Abruzzi" John Abruzzi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.89,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"John Abruzzi" John Abruzzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.19,0:10:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you wanna see Burrows
so bad anyhow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he's my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They denied the motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.89,0:11:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,May 11th.
That's the date, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the date they,
uh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,execute me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.85,0:11:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't
kill that man, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The evidence says you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care
what the evidence says.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Swear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.12,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear to you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did they get it wrong then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The courts,
the appeals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know. Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All I keep thinking,
looking back on it is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.97,0:12:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I was set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And whoever it was
that set me up
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,wants me in the ground
as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's another word
for "love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the context?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.65,0:12:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The "I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't never knocking over
a liquor store again" context.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Except, you know, classy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.61,0:12:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm proposing to my girl,
if you gotta know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.66,0:12:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,In a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a better way?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Face-to-face
works pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.37,0:12:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This place ain't exactly
the romantic spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have her get
on the Staten Island Ferry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, once she can see
the Empire State Building,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.63,0:12:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,she opens the letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like almost being there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for the fact
that I won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Try "passion."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! Ooh! "Passion."
"Passion." That's dope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.85,0:12:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you spell that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Is it P-A-S-H?
-Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No "H"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,LJ, hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.37,0:13:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can
go through with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's going
to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand
each other, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yeah.
-Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Saturday.
Not Sunday. Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want hundreds,
I don't want fives, I don't want ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tens and 20s only.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Abruzzi, I need you
to hire me a P.I.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you ought to hear
what I got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You got nothing I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't be
too sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.83,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.13,0:14:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what I need... a duck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.05,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,P.I., Abruzzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You might find I can be
of more assistance than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mull it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come find me
when you're ready to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, guys,
pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get home tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maggio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah? So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the son of a bitch
that fingered Abruzzi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Fibonacci?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.50,0:15:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the punk
was gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Evidently,
somebody found him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody messing with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This you're not
going to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.48,0:15:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Tattoo looks fresh.
Hold that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess, being a diabetic,
you don't mind needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.28,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Michael, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Scofield.
I read your report.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tancredi will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tancredi" like the governor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not related,
are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Wouldn't think
you'd find the daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of Frontier Justice Frank
working in a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.17,0:16:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,As a doctor, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in being part
of the solution, not the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. "Be the change you want
to see in the world."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. That was just
my senior quote.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole time,
I was thinking it was Gandhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit tight.
Put direct pressure on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.57,0:16:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back
in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how do we play this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You hook me up
with a few weeks' supply?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try.
No hypos on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the farthest thing
from a junkie. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.93,0:17:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I got news
for you, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Trust me" means absolutely zero
inside these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The only way
you're getting that insulin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.23,0:17:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,is if I'm administering it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll be seeing
a lot of each other, then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.46,0:17:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all clear
on the Burrows execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.71,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,-Good.
-Except for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bishop McMorrow
is not in the fold.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got a lot of influence
with the governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They went to prep school
together, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the closer it gets,
the more I'm worried
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that the bottom is going
to fall out of this whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it's time you arranged a visit
with the good bishop, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, in one month,
it'll all be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Son of Man must be delivered
into the hands of sinful men
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.28,0:18:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and be crucified
and the third day, rise again."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And they remembered His words,
and so should you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day, gentlemen.
May God be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go,
let's go, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.69,0:18:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go. Come on, man.
Keep moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep moving.
Move. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why?
- Let's go, man. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting you
out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Burrows, roll it up.
Happy hour's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you designed
the place, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Too formal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Too "greeting card."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we got
to make a decision
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,sooner or later,
you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, at some point,
we got to pull the trigger on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want
to rush this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only going
to do it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.73,0:19:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to
get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, can I
ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you putting this off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.12,0:19:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, are you
having second thoughts?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Honey, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.71,0:19:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-I just can't help thinking this is about--
-It's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I want
to be your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Passion?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.22,0:19:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you went for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She probably thinks
I went sissy up in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,"Passion." You know,
got more than one syllable, too much talkin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:19:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me from now on.
One-syllable Sucre.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. No. Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.65,0:20:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hate. Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I proposed to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't take time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Si or no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One syllable, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's supposed
to come around
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,for a conjugal on Tuesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always
calling me beforehand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,letting me know
she's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, man,
I ain't heard a peep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You spooked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Scofield.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together.
Pope wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No good, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No one gets an audience
with the Pope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.23,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not unless he's real interested
in what you got going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.19,0:20:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Top of your class at Loyola.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Magna cum laude, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help wondering
what someone with your credentials
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is doing in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Took a wrong turn
a few months back, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound
like a traffic infraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Like all you did was turn the wrong way
up a one-way street.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone turns up one
sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason
I called you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed in your I-file,
under occupation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you put down "unemployed."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true, now, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're
a structural engineer, Scofield.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shah Jahan
built the Taj Majal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,as a monument
to his undying love for his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife is quite fond
of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It appeals
to the romantic in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Being married to someone
in Corrections, terrible job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't wish it on anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.76,0:21:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, in 39 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.18,0:21:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,my wife
has never complained.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the worst part of it is,
I've never thanked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.73,0:21:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So, because
I couldn't say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.23,0:21:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, you know,
I could build it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Come June,
it's our 40th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You see,
the problem is,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I build anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,it's all gonna come down
like a house of cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I was hoping
you could be of assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For the favor,
I can offer you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.92,0:22:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,three days of work
a week in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.71,0:22:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll keep you
off the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.76,0:22:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.97,0:22:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Son, it's better for me
to owe you one in here
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.48,0:22:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,than it is for you
to owe me one,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.85,0:22:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.95,0:22:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Two pounds of pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you trying to do,
set a record?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.62,0:22:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not funny, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:22:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be going
to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.12,0:23:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious to me
you need some guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.88,0:23:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,From who,
old Daddy Warbucks?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him a chance.
He's a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We got nothing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.39,0:23:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Where is this
coming from, LJ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.77,0:23:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Last semester you were getting
almost all A's and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your father, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.28,0:23:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't an immaculate
conception, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time
we went and saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.08,0:23:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.83,0:23:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about as excited
by the prospect as you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.33,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but something's gotta give.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You have got
too much potential
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.50,0:23:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to be screwing up
your life like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.38,0:23:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they'd sent you
to Taylorville or Marion and not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.51,0:23:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'd be doing
the same thing I'm doing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating Jell-O,
drinking Kool-Aid...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.10,0:24:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the luck of the draw
that you're in here with Lincoln.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.90,0:24:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You forget I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.61,0:24:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You two have the most
dysfunctional idea of love I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.90,0:24:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What, he beats you up
to keep you off the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.53,0:24:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so you get yourself tossed
into Fox River with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.54,0:24:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.17,0:24:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.25,0:24:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved him
as much as you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.21,0:24:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Past tense for you, maybe.
Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.55,0:24:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave him a shot
when I got back from college. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.67,0:24:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with all the stuff
that was going on with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.43,0:24:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I did everything I could
to make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.22,0:24:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And he threw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.51,0:24:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You ever think maybe he was hurt
that you left
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.22,0:24:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.39,0:24:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.02,0:24:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is you're doing,
don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.90,0:24:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.94,0:24:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already appealing
your case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.19,0:24:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you
to leave that alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.02,0:24:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten in touch with the diocese about Lincoln.
The bishop may be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.86,0:24:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't stop it.
It'll only delay it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.24,0:24:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You want
to do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.58,0:25:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You find out
who's trying to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.29,0:25:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody's trying to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.42,0:25:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The evidence was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.13,0:25:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The evidence was cooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.38,0:25:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Visiting hours
are now over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.76,0:25:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.27,0:25:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone wants him
dead, Veronica.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.56,0:25:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Something more
is going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.40,0:25:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is desperation, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.69,0:25:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're grabbing at straws.
You're in denial.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.82,0:25:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.73,0:25:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't watch him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.78,0:25:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.98,0:26:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.31,0:26:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about the Burrows situation
that I can help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.23,0:26:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our understanding
that you have great influence with the governor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.23,0:26:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say it's "great" or "influence."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.82,0:26:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.16,0:26:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also our understanding
that you oppose the death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man of God.
How could I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.95,0:26:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, we're hoping
you'll suspend that position.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.25,0:26:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,At least temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If the inmate appeals
to me for intervention,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.04,0:26:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,how can I
turn my back on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.59,0:26:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a habit of answering
a question with a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.63,0:26:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have a way of asking questions
that beg more questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.64,0:26:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying
you won't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.23,0:26:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a man to equivocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.73,0:26:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're, what, 62 years old now,
Your Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:26:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.90,0:26:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would assume, then,
that you'd be well-versed
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.36,0:27:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in how our government's
tax system works.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.36,0:27:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking personal
capital gains
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,under the church's
tax shelter...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.33,0:27:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be fraud,
wouldn't it, Your Excellency?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.62,0:27:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not be cowed
into forsaking my beliefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.13,0:27:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Not by you or anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.17,0:27:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.34,0:27:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good day, Excellency.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.92,0:27:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kellerman...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.43,0:27:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it about this case
that the Secret Service is so interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.72,0:27:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The man killed
the Vice President's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.07,0:27:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.03,0:27:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.11,0:27:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone found Fibonacci.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.78,0:27:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking at the photos
right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.78,0:27:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch
has got a beard, sunglasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.28,0:27:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Witness protection,
if I ever saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.54,0:27:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was this someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.95,0:27:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know, there's no return address
on the envelope.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.92,0:27:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.13,0:27:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,this folded-up bird
made of paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.09,0:28:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like origami?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.47,0:28:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.30,0:28:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like origami.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.79,0:28:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Charles Westmoreland,
right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.09,0:28:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.21,0:28:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew your wife
before she passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.93,0:28:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew Marla?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.01,0:28:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Ann?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.97,0:28:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.35,0:28:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We taught together
in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.31,0:28:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,East Farmington.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.43,0:28:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean West Wilmington?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.02,0:28:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No more tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.81,0:28:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.23,0:28:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems you know
everything about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.69,0:29:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.61,0:29:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael Scofield.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.32,0:29:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you get it in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.20,0:29:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,First off,
she's not an "it."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.41,0:29:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She's Marilyn,
and she's grandfathered
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.66,0:29:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,back from the days
when prisoners were allowed a creature comfort or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.66,0:29:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard
you were D.B. Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.21,0:29:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Every new fish
comes in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.17,0:29:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,first thing they hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.38,0:29:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is that Charles Westmoreland
is D.B. Cooper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.34,0:29:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you
like I tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.55,0:29:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You want the Cooper story?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.51,0:29:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give it to you,
'cause I'm not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.85,0:29:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.77,0:29:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of wish it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.60,0:29:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The man's a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.02,0:29:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nowhere near as much
as I wish it were true, friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.02,0:29:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd have a million-five
waiting for me on the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.86,0:29:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd put some grass
under 'em if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.57,0:29:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing would go
a whole lot easier if you'd just hire me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.20,0:29:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.83,0:29:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Say you were able
to get outside those walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.75,0:29:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,would you have
the people in place
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.92,0:30:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure
you disappeared forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.05,0:30:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.46,0:30:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.05,0:30:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Fibonacci?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.72,0:30:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the way
it works.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.93,0:30:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They come at me, John,
I'm coming after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.10,0:30:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.52,0:30:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, fight, fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.42,0:30:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.14,0:30:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.93,0:30:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally
misjudged you, Scofield.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.02,0:31:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think
you were the agitating type.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.48,0:31:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Behavior like that
will not be tolerated in my prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.48,0:31:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninety days in the SHU!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.69,0:31:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That ought to be enough time
to convince you of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.78,0:31:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ninety days?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.70,0:31:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.79,0:31:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.00,0:31:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.13,0:31:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not of much value
to you in the SHU.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.42,0:31:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Value?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.34,0:31:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... The Taj.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.46,0:31:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a shame
for the eighth wonder of the modern world
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.55,0:31:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to collapse because the stress
isn't properly propagated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.76,0:31:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Properly propagated?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.93,0:31:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Properly propagated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.72,0:31:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The joints are overloaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.35,0:31:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't provide anywhere
near the sheer strength
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.73,0:31:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the completed structure
will need.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.81,0:31:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How much work
are we talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.02,0:31:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You want it by when, June?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.44,0:31:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.57,0:31:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'd better get started,
wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.39,0:32:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.87,0:32:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Bishop McMorrow
was killed last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.91,0:32:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone shot him
while he was sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.87,0:32:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought
you'd want to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.92,0:32:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.55,0:32:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Michael was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.54,0:33:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sink, you got a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.97,0:33:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He was arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.97,0:33:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.27,0:33:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Possession of marijuana.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.81,0:33:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured he could use
some fatherly advice before it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.40,0:33:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,-Gone forever?
-I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.69,0:33:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.11,0:33:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Lisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.95,0:33:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.29,0:34:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Dope, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.79,0:34:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Using or dealing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.62,0:34:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.96,0:34:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what, you, uh, think it gives you
some kind of street cred?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.30,0:34:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a piece
of the good life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.63,0:34:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Take advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.97,0:34:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.55,0:34:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.22,0:34:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She drags me in here,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.22,0:34:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you give me a big speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.68,0:34:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I walk away a changed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.77,0:34:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Straight A's.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.10,0:34:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard.
Grow up and be a dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.02,0:34:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.86,0:34:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to realize
who's getting punished
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.15,0:34:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're doing
the things you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.99,0:34:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's me.
It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.82,0:34:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.28,0:34:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Punished the old man
'cause he was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.83,0:34:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what it got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.00,0:34:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not asking you
to love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.46,0:34:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I already screwed up
that chance long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.46,0:34:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you
to love yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.76,0:34:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can still put the brakes
on this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.05,0:35:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what
fatherly advice is like.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.47,0:35:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.72,0:35:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I got homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.02,0:35:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They're putting me
to death, LJ.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.15,0:35:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In a month's time,
I'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.86,0:35:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.82,0:35:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already
dead to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.97,0:35:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.60,0:35:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You mean "yes," yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.60,0:35:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.73,0:35:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah!
- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.48,0:35:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh, there's just one thing.
-Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.65,0:35:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama wants us to wait
till you get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.11,0:35:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, mi amor.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.28,0:35:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we have
to get married in a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.57,0:36:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay. Esta bien.
-A Catholic church.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.74,0:36:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't want to mess
with the Catholic roots, would we?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.75,0:36:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to Loyola.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.91,0:36:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been
checking up on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.42,0:36:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I like to get to know
my patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.33,0:36:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Northwestern.
Graduated two years after you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.42,0:36:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we met before,
you know, drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.05,0:36:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,out at a bar somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.51,0:36:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.68,0:36:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,-That a compliment?
-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.72,0:36:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.89,0:36:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.10,0:36:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your blood glucose is at
50 milligrams per deciliter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.85,0:36:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-So?
-That's hypoglycemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body's reacting
to the insulin
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.61,0:36:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,like you're not a diabetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.77,0:36:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sure it's type 1 diabetes
you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.86,0:36:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.44,0:36:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.61,0:36:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Not experiencing
any tingling sensation, cold sweats--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.87,0:36:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.37,0:36:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.75,0:36:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.79,0:36:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I did and I do.
I need them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.71,0:37:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Um, great.
Well, I'll call him after lunch, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.47,0:37:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
I'm with a patient. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.55,0:37:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to run some tests
next time you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.89,0:37:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Last thing I want is to be
administering insulin to a man who doesn't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.60,0:37:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.77,0:37:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.73,0:37:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you get here,
by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.65,0:37:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.16,0:37:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
That's why I asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.82,0:37:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You know. Hector.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.49,0:37:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.49,0:37:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have any money
for the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.20,0:37:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,so he offered me a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.04,0:37:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He was really sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.33,0:37:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Honey, he's just a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.04,0:37:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not
just a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.13,0:37:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know Hector.
I know men.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.09,0:37:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Men and women
can't be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.38,0:37:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A guy doesn't drive a girl
500 miles across state lines
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.22,0:37:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,because he wants
to be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.43,0:37:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Casanova, wrap it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.56,0:37:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you got nothing
to worry about, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.23,0:37:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you I'm marrying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.35,0:37:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not you
I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.73,0:38:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixteen more months.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.03,0:38:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.96,0:38:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Be easy, son, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.93,0:38:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sucre tells me
you're the local pharmacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.15,0:38:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-What you need, man?
-PUGNAc.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.36,0:38:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I only speak English,
white boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.61,0:38:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an insulin blocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Standard
over-the-counter variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.61,0:38:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get it
at any pharmacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.78,0:38:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can get that
at medical then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.20,0:38:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get it at medical.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.37,0:38:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.37,0:38:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because they're already
giving me insulin shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.25,0:38:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one mixed-up cracker,
you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.91,0:39:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get it for me,
or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.25,0:39:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if you tell me
why is it you want
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.29,0:39:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep going
back up to medical
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.59,0:39:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to get an insulin shot
for which you don't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.13,0:39:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the ambiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.80,0:39:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.51,0:39:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we in business?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.81,0:39:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Facility Two lockdown
in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.10,0:39:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Facility One lockdown
in ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.53,0:39:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Scofield. I don't know
what you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.82,0:39:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,but Abruzzi wanted me
to give you this P.I. card.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.99,0:39:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.03,0:39:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You just joined the ranks
of the employed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.55,0:39:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudos, Fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.60,0:39:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You got spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.85,0:40:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, cons,
break it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.44,0:40:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Move it, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.04,0:40:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw Veronica
came by yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.21,0:40:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Still engaged to that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.42,0:40:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.04,0:40:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could have been me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.04,0:40:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't
self-destructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.92,0:40:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You think I meant
to knock up Lisa Rix?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.63,0:40:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just being stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.09,0:40:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.55,0:40:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't have
pushed her away, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.18,0:40:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You pushed everyone away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.06,0:40:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an anchor.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.56,0:40:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All I'll do
is drag him down with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.73,0:40:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you hire him?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.36,0:40:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your friends close
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.82,0:40:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and your enemies closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.33,0:41:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean
what you said earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.66,0:41:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not here on vacation,
trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.25,0:41:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting outside these walls,
that's just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.42,0:41:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to need money.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.26,0:41:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.97,0:41:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And people
on the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.76,0:41:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,People that can
help you disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.14,0:41:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.43,0:41:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They just
don't know it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.27,0:41:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, whatever you got
going on, fill me in,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.27,0:41:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause I'm in the dark here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.44,0:41:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chaparral Associates
got the contract
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.40,0:41:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to retrofit
this place in '99.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.20,0:41:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Four million dollar contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.62,0:41:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Head partner
couldn't crack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.28,0:41:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, he subcontracted out,
an under-the-table sort of deal
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.41,0:41:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,with a former associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.66,0:41:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy was one
of the partners in my firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.58,0:41:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We basically ghost-wrote
the whole plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.17,0:41:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Crossed the t's, dotted the i's,
grouted the tiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.64,0:42:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen the blueprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.97,0:42:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.56,0:42:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got them on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.32,0:42:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.99,0:42:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to be seeing
something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.16,0:42:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.36,0:43:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Captioned by Point.360.
